  "intro": "<p>  </p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, \" e;helvetica=\"\" neue\"e;,=\"\" e;pingfang=\"\" sc\"e;,=\"\" e;hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\"e;,=\"\" e;microsoft=\"\" yahei\"e;,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 22.4px;=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" !important;=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" !important;\"=\"\" span=\"\" 《西游记》这部经典名著，曾融入了国内几代孩子们成长的故事，80、90、直到这个年代，还记得那部经典的剧作吗？经典是因为它汇聚了我们传统文化的精髓，更展现了华夏儿女的古老信仰，相信太多中国的古城都拥有佛塔，它是我们祖先遗留下来善与爱的结晶，象征着守护，守护那一方水土。=\"\" p=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">         善音歌者---桑吉平措今昔再次重演来自我们回味的时光中，家喻户晓的经典名剧《西游记》里的名曲---《清空月儿明》（扫塔歌），一次全新演绎，再现那段美好时光，让你我静静地回味，回味着我们古老的城市，古老的建筑和先人大爱的遗留。可这“扫塔”，又何尝不是扫我们的内心呢？这值得反思的人生，正是一步一台阶的成长啊。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, \" e;helvetica=\"\" neue\"e;,=\"\" e;pingfang=\"\" sc\"e;,=\"\" e;hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\"e;,=\"\" e;microsoft=\"\" yahei\"e;,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" line-height:=\"\" 22.4px;=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" !important;=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" !important;\"=\"\" span=\"\" br=\"\" p=\"\">     <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"> 《晴空月儿明》（又名《扫塔歌》）让我们扫除世间一切恶，留存那一切真、善、美。</span></p>\n\n<p> </p>",
